                    <comment id="12972875" author="mikemccand" created="Sat, 18 Dec 2010 21:58:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I changed CMS.sync to .join() to any still-alive threads, and changed MergeThread to not remove itself from mergeThreads but rather updateMergeThread to prune any dead threads.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
